Detailed Description

cvmx_pcsx::_tx_rx_polarity_reg

RX lane polarity vector [3:0] = XOR_RXPLRT<9:6> ^ [4[RXPLRT<1>]]; TX lane polarity vector [3:0] = XOR_TXPLRT<5:2> ^ [4[TXPLRT<0>]]; In short keep <1:0> to 2'b00, and use <5:2> and <9:6> fields to define per lane polarities
